" - [#2]: Yukio Ohashi and Wayne Orchiston. The evolution of local Southeast Asian astronomy and the influence of China, India, the Islamic World and the West. In W Orchiston and M N Vahia, editors, Exploring the History of Southeast Asian Astronomy, pages 673–767. Springer, Cham, 2021.\n"
